        "Region": 3,
        "CharacterDialogInfo_List": [
          {
            "CharacterId": 10035,
            "CostumeUniqueId": 1003501,
            "DisplayOrder": 350,
            "DialogCategory": 8,
            "DialogCondition": 0,
            "GroupId": 1,
            "ActionName": "",
            "DialogType": 0,
            "Duration": 14333,
            "LocalizeKR": "가, 감사합니다. 선생님.\n그…… 챙겨 주셔서……",
            "LocalizeJP": "あ、ありがとうございました、\n先生……その、\n助かりました……。",
            "VoiceIds": [],
            "CollectionVisible": false,
            "CVCollectionType": 0,
            "LocalizeCVGroup": "CVGroup_UILobbySpecial_Idle1",
            "AnimationName": "Talk_01_M",
            "Anniversary": 0,
            "StartDate": "",
            "EndDate": "",
            "ApplyPosition": false,
            "PosX": 0.0,
            "PosY": 0.0,
            "UnlockFavorRank": 0,
            "UnlockEquipWeapon": false
          },
          {
            "CharacterId": 10035,
            "CostumeUniqueId": 1003501,
            "DisplayOrder": 360,
            "DialogCategory": 8,
            "DialogCondition": 0,
            "GroupId": 2,
            "ActionName": "",
            "DialogType": 0,
            "Duration": 10500,
            "LocalizeKR": "……이거, 말인가요?\n저기, 해독 작업 중이었어요.",
            "LocalizeJP": "……これ、ですか？\nえっと、解読作業を\nしていまして。",
            "VoiceIds": [],
            "CollectionVisible": false,
            "CVCollectionType": 0,
            "LocalizeCVGroup": "CVGroup_UILobbySpecial_Idle2",
            "AnimationName": "Talk_02_M",
            "Anniversary": 0,
            "StartDate": "",
            "EndDate": "",
            "ApplyPosition": false,
            "PosX": 0.0,
            "PosY": 0.0,
            "UnlockFavorRank": 0,
            "UnlockEquipWeapon": false
          },
          {
            "CharacterId": 10035,
            "CostumeUniqueId": 1003501,
            "DisplayOrder": 370,
            "DialogCategory": 8,
            "DialogCondition": 0,
            "GroupId": 2,
            "ActionName": "",
            "DialogType": 0,
            "Duration": 11000,
            "LocalizeKR": "이 고서관에는……\n옛날 말로 쓰여진 책이,\n많이 있어요.",
            "LocalizeJP": "この古書館には……\n昔の言葉で書かれた本が、\nたくさんあるんです。",
            "VoiceIds": [],
            "CollectionVisible": false,
            "CVCollectionType": 0,
            "LocalizeCVGroup": "CVGroup_UILobbySpecial_Idle2",
            "AnimationName": "",
            "Anniversary": 0,
            "StartDate": "",
            "EndDate": "",
            "ApplyPosition": false,
            "PosX": 0.0,
            "PosY": 0.0,
            "UnlockFavorRank": 0,
            "UnlockEquipWeapon": false
          },
          {
            "CharacterId": 10035,
            "CostumeUniqueId": 1003501,
            "DisplayOrder": 380,
            "DialogCategory": 8,
            "DialogCondition": 0,
            "GroupId": 3,
            "ActionName": "",
            "DialogType": 0,
            "Duration": 10900,
            "LocalizeKR": "이 아이들도, 누군가에게\n전하고 싶은 것들을 품은 채,\n기다리고 있었을 텐데……",
            "LocalizeJP": "この子たちも、\n誰かに伝えたいことを\n抱えたまま、待っている\nはずなので……。",
            "VoiceIds": [],
            "CollectionVisible": false,
            "CVCollectionType": 0,
            "LocalizeCVGroup": "CVGroup_UILobbySpecial_Idle3",
            "AnimationName": "Talk_03_M",
            "Anniversary": 0,
            "StartDate": "",
            "EndDate": "",
            "ApplyPosition": false,
            "PosX": 0.0,
            "PosY": 0.0,
            "UnlockFavorRank": 0,
            "UnlockEquipWeapon": false
          },
          {
            "CharacterId": 10035,
            "CostumeUniqueId": 1003501,
            "DisplayOrder": 390,
            "DialogCategory": 8,
            "DialogCondition": 0,
            "GroupId": 3,
            "ActionName": "",
            "DialogType": 0,
            "Duration": 10267,
            "LocalizeKR": "달리 할 사람도 없고요……\n그래서, 제가……",
            "LocalizeJP": "他にやる人もいませんし……\nそれで、私が……。",
            "VoiceIds": [],
            "CollectionVisible": false,
            "CVCollectionType": 0,
            "LocalizeCVGroup": "CVGroup_UILobbySpecial_Idle3",
            "AnimationName": "",
            "Anniversary": 0,
            "StartDate": "",
            "EndDate": "",
            "ApplyPosition": false,
            "PosX": 0.0,
            "PosY": 0.0,
            "UnlockFavorRank": 0,
            "UnlockEquipWeapon": false
          },
          {
            "CharacterId": 10035,
            "CostumeUniqueId": 1003501,
            "DisplayOrder": 400,
            "DialogCategory": 8,
            "DialogCondition": 0,
            "GroupId": 4,
            "ActionName": "",
            "DialogType": 0,
            "Duration": 9167,
            "LocalizeKR": "……죄송해요.\n재미없는 이야기……였죠?",
            "LocalizeJP": "……すみません、\n面白くない話……でしたよね？",
            "VoiceIds": [],
            "CollectionVisible": false,
            "CVCollectionType": 0,
            "LocalizeCVGroup": "CVGroup_UILobbySpecial_Idle4",
            "AnimationName": "Talk_04_M",
            "Anniversary": 0,
            "StartDate": "",
            "EndDate": "",
            "ApplyPosition": false,
            "PosX": 0.0,
            "PosY": 0.0,
            "UnlockFavorRank": 0,
            "UnlockEquipWeapon": false
          },
          {
            "CharacterId": 10035,
            "CostumeUniqueId": 1003501,
            "DisplayOrder": 410,
            "DialogCategory": 8,
            "DialogCondition": 0,
            "GroupId": 5,
            "ActionName": "",
            "DialogType": 0,
            "Duration": 12800,
            "LocalizeKR": "……!! 어, 그게, 그……\n그, 그렇게까지 칭찬해\n주시면 그……",
            "LocalizeJP": "……っ！あ、えっと、その……\nそこまで褒めていただけると、\nその……。",
            "VoiceIds": [],
            "CollectionVisible": false,
            "CVCollectionType": 0,
            "LocalizeCVGroup": "CVGroup_UILobbySpecial_Idle5",
            "AnimationName": "Talk_05_M",
            "Anniversary": 0,
            "StartDate": "",
            "EndDate": "",
            "ApplyPosition": false,
            "PosX": 0.0,
            "PosY": 0.0,
            "UnlockFavorRank": 0,
            "UnlockEquipWeapon": false
          },
          {
            "CharacterId": 10035,
            "CostumeUniqueId": 1003501,
            "DisplayOrder": 420,
            "DialogCategory": 8,
            "DialogCondition": 0,
            "GroupId": 5,
            "ActionName": "",
            "DialogType": 0,
            "Duration": 15200,
            "LocalizeKR": "무슨 말씀을 드려야 좋을지……\n말이, 잘 떠오르지 않네요……\n흐……",
            "LocalizeJP": "何と返せば良いのか……\n言葉が、見つからなくなって\nしまいますね……ふふっ……。",
            "VoiceIds": [],
            "CollectionVisible": false,
            "CVCollectionType": 0,
            "LocalizeCVGroup": "CVGroup_UILobbySpecial_Idle5",
            "AnimationName": "",
            "Anniversary": 0,
